WEBVTT

00:00.952 --> 00:03.004
<i>This glove once belonged</i>
<i>to Roberto Clemente.</i>

00:03.104 --> 00:04.054
Thought Jamie
might like it.

00:04.193 --> 00:05.275
Are you sure
about this, man?

00:05.370 --> 00:06.403
That glove belongs
on the hand

00:06.455 --> 00:07.621
of someone
who loves the game.

00:07.705 --> 00:09.239
Me, I used to stand
out in right field

00:09.291 --> 00:10.558
and chase butterflies.

00:10.625 --> 00:12.426
What if I told you
there was a college prospect

00:12.494 --> 00:15.262
who threw 98 miles an hour
accurately?

00:15.347 --> 00:17.098
There must be a reason
he doesn't have an Agent.

00:17.182 --> 00:19.133
Well, what if I told you
his name was Kellerman?

00:19.217 --> 00:21.385
As in
Professor Kellerman's son.

00:21.436 --> 00:22.436
Oh, wow.
I love it.

00:22.521 --> 00:23.754
It's to wear
with your gray suit

00:23.805 --> 00:26.089
when you get that reporter job
at the station.

00:26.141 --> 00:27.641
Thank you.

00:27.726 --> 00:29.193
Oh, it's the station.

00:29.260 --> 00:31.195
It's for you.

00:32.981 --> 00:34.565
I think
we should adopt.

00:34.616 --> 00:37.568
I want that so much,
and I want it with you.

00:37.636 --> 00:39.370
But are you sure
we're ready?

00:39.437 --> 00:40.871
Yeah. We're ready.

