09:31.209 --> 09:32.760
Oh, yeah?

09:34.429 --> 09:36.514
I gotcha,
you crazy tigger-y thing.

09:36.565 --> 09:38.232
Mm, I like it
when you get me.

09:38.317 --> 09:40.318
